1
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:10,940
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:14,900
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:17,580
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,580
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:25,460
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:31,580
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:35,420
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,100
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:44,420
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:50,820
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:54,980
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:05,660
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:12,460
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:17,460
=Episode 17=

17
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,120
Mr. Lu Said

18
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:22,120
as long as you're still breathing,
you're just in the way.

19
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:23,760
Best if you were dead.

20
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,880
My lady! My lady!

21
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,520
Bad news, my lady!

22
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,000
My lady!

23
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,640
Wlow down.

24
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:18,120
There's a catastrophe, my lady!

25
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,920
What's with all this flapping about?

26
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:21,120
Catch your breath before you speak.

27
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,360
Can I talk now, my lady?

28
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:27,400
Of course. Spit it out.

29
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,160
Your husband...

30
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:28,760
Have you forgotten?

31
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,240
Li Yunhe and I

32
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,160
are already divorced.

33
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,880
He's not part
of the Zhou family anymore.

34
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,520
That's not the point, my lady.

35
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,280
Mr. Li

36
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,880
has accepted Long Er's challenge.

37
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:38,680
They're going to settle it in the arena.

38
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,920
They even signed a liability waiver.

39
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:40,800
What?

40
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,680
Who is he fighting in the arena?

41
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:43,840
Long Er,

42
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,880
the guy who's always tailing

43
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:46,000
the Marquis's heir.

44
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:46,960
My lady!

45
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,000
Where are you going, my lady?

46
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,120
To find Li Yunhe.

47
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,080
Wait up!

48
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:52,680
I heard

49
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,160
Mr. Li of Xianquan Tavern

50
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:55,480
is going to fight Long Er in the arena.

51
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:56,400
Let's go check it out.

52
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,200
Yeah.

53
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:58,960
Yunzhuo,

54
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:01,000
has Li Yunhe completely lost his mind?

55
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,200
He's nothing but a bookworm.

56
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,480
What's he doing fighting Long Er?

57
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,400
You're that worried about him?

58
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,000
Don't tell me
you've gone and fallen for him.

59
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,880
What kind of nonsense is that?

60
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,200
I'm just afraid
Long Er will beat him to a pulp.

61
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,000
And I wouldn't

62
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:14,200
be able to find anyone
this entertaining, that's all.

63
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:14,600
Yunzhuo,

64
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,920
Li Yunhe definitely can't beat Long Er.

65
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,600
Why don't you send in the Shadow Guards

66
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:20,880
and just kill Long Er first?

67
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,320
Don't worry.

68
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,280
Li Yunhe is full of tricks and schemes.

69
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,920
He never does anything he isn't sure of.

70
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,600
As for this arena fight,

71
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:29,200
maybe he's got another angle.

72
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,880
He's already in the arena

73
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,600
and with a signed liability waiver,
no less.

74
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:33,600
What other angle could there be?

75
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,320
And don't you forget,

76
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,880
that guy is one
of the Marquis House's men.

77
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:37,960
Lu Qifeng can't wait

78
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,280
for Li Yunhe to drop dead sooner.

79
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:39,960
And what is he doing?

80
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,600
He's practically serving up his own life
on a platter.

81
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:46,840
They say
Long Er is a martial arts fanatic.

82
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,800
His fists can shatter stone tablets.

83
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:51,240
Is it possible that with a single punch,

84
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,160
he can just

85
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,400
beat Li Yunhe to death?

86
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,080
Quite possible.

87
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:56,280
Long Er is a genuine, top-tier fighter.

88
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:57,920
What a shame.

89
00:03:57,920 --> 00:04:00,280
Li Yunhe is just too reckless.

90
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,240
In reciting poems and matching verses,

91
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,840
he's truly unmatched.

92
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:04,160
But he's just

93
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,960
a frail scholar
who couldn't truss up a chicken.

94
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,160
How could he
possibly be Long Er's match?

95
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,080
Sir.

96
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,920
Ladies and gentlemen,

97
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,080
dear honored guests,

98
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:21,080
folks of Feng City,

99
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,200
today's arena match

100
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,120
features

101
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:26,360
Li Yunhe, the owner of Xianquan Tavern,

102
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,520
versus Long Er!

103
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,480
Let's give a roaring welcome

104
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,400
as they make their grand entrance!

105
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:34,680
- Yeah!
- Yeah!

106
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,520
And now,

107
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,360
let's have

108
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:41,200
both fighters sign the liability waiver.

109
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,280
Move it.

110
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,520
You think I'd fear you?

111
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,040
Don't we still have an ad to finish?

112
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:52,760
Oh, right.

113
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,880
A big thanks to Xianquan Tavern

114
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:59,200
for sponsoring today's arena match.

115
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,320
Delicious and pricey.

116
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,960
Absolutely not a bargain
in the slightest.

117
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:03,400
For stir-fried dishes
bursting with flavor,

118
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:05,320
head on down to Xianquan Tavern.

119
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,400
Nice!

120
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,720
This guy really knows
how to stir the pot.

121
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,720
Doesn't let up for a single moment.

122
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:38,340
(Liability Waiver Signatory: Long Er)

123
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,520
Out of my way! Move it!

124
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,600
Out of the way! Move it, now!

125
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,800
Have a seat, my lord.

126
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:18,400
Excuse me, let us through!

127
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:20,080
Yunzhuo, look over there.

128
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:22,800
Li Yunhe!

129
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,600
Don't sign it!

130
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:28,840
(I knew)

131
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:30,520
(Yu would come today.)

132
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,000
Li Yunhe, have you got a death wish?

133
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,920
Mr. Li, don't sign it!

134
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,600
(The fact that you came today)

135
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,400
(means you do care about me after all.)

136
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,880
Do you hear me?

137
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,560
That's a liability waiver
you're signing!

138
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,280
You can't beat him!

139
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:43,320
Get down from there, now!

140
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,360
I get it.

141
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:45,960
Li Yunhe

142
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:47,520
agreed to this arena fight with Long Er

143
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:48,520
solely

144
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:51,080
to lure Zhou Xingyu out into the open.

145
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,600
He's risking his own life

146
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,360
just to see Zhou Xingyu one more time?

147
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,280
Is it worth it?

148
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,320
I don't know

149
00:06:58,320 --> 00:06:59,720
what he's got up his sleeve
to beat Long Er.

150
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,080
But what I do know

151
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,600
is that he won't lose.

152
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:11,380
(Liability Waiver)

153
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:14,420
(Signatory: Li Yunhe)

154
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,120
What a pathetic, disgraceful farce.

155
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,120
Seems Li Yunhe has been

156
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:21,600
utterly cast aside by the Zhou family.

157
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:25,400
Without the Zhous meddling,

158
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,680
once Long Er makes his move,

159
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:29,720
Li Yunhe is as good as dead.

160
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:31,320
Congratulations, my lord.

161
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:32,480
You've won.

162
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,880
Once this eyesore is dead,

163
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,160
the Zhou family's fortune
and Zhou Xingyu

164
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:38,480
will all fall right into

165
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,800
your waiting hands.

166
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:42,120
My lord,

167
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:43,400
someone's opened a betting pool.

168
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,480
Care to get in on it?

169
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:46,720
What are the odds?

170
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:50,440
1 to 2?

171
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,080
1 to 20.

172
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:53,000
If Li Yunhe wins,

173
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:53,680
it's a 20 times payout.

174
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:59,240
Not going to play a little, Mr. Chen?

175
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,800
What are you hesitating for?

176
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,640
An unknown outcome? That's gambling.

177
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:06,240
A known outcome? That's investing.

178
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:08,280
Opportunities like this
don't come around often.

179
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,400
Then I'll just put up

180
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:12,200
my entire savings.

181
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,960
Every little bit of profit helps.

182
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,760
My lord, aren't you going to buy in?

183
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,040
This is a guaranteed win.

184
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:21,000
(I arranged this match myself.)

185
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,800
(You think I don't know
Long Er is bound to win?)

186
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,640
(If I actually had any money,)

187
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:26,360
(wouldn't I have bet it all?)

188
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:29,560
My lord, you're really not
putting anything down?

189
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,880
The match is about to start.

190
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,000
(If it weren't for Li Yunhe,)

191
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,880
(when I hoarded grain last time,)

192
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:38,680
(I would have raked in a fortune.)

193
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:40,200
(No way I'd be so broke)

194
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,400
(that I could barely jingle like now.)

195
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,960
Since the liability waiver
is now signed,

196
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:49,480
(Treasures of Heaven)
let the match begin!

197
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,400
Li Yunhe, you can't beat him!

198
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,400
Come back!

199
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,440
Yu,

200
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:57,080
to see your face one more time
before I die,

201
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,840
I'm already content.

202
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,480
With Long Er making his move,

203
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,720
Li Yunhe,

204
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,960
let's see if you live through this.

205
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,320
- Watch out!
- Watch out!

206
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,480
What kind of fist technique is that?

207
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:50,680
Wing Chun. My unique style.

208
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:52,720
Wing what?

209
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,720
Never heard of it.

210
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:56,680
Black Tiger Heart Strike!

211
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:10,880
Yeah!

212
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:13,840
Hit him! Go on!

213
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,160
Oops.

214
00:10:21,160 --> 00:10:21,920
Sorry.

215
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:23,120
Can anyone kindly tell me

216
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,840
what on earth Long Er is doing?

217
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,160
Just go hit him!

218
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:46,080
Go on!

219
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,640
Take my punch!

220
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,200
Isn't Long Er

221
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:04,040
Lu Qifeng's right-hand man?

222
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:05,400
Why is he

223
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,280
putting on an act with Li Yunhe?

224
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:08,840
I knew this guy

225
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,160
was up to some new shenanigans.

226
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,400
Why is the way Mr. Li fights

227
00:11:12,400 --> 00:11:13,960
so different from everyone else?

228
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,040
Yunzhuo,

229
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,480
is Li Yunhe

230
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,400
fixing the match?

231
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:23,640
Seems like it.

232
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:26,360
From what we've seen so far,

233
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:27,360
the two of them

234
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,440
have definitely reached
some kind of agreement.

235
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,800
But I've got no idea

236
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:32,960
what kind of bargaining chip

237
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,320
Li Yunhe could have offered
the Marquis House

238
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,360
to make them willing

239
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:38,360
to play along with this charade.

240
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:40,040
Could it be

241
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:42,160
the manufacturing process
for Gambiered Silk?

242
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:45,400
What you're saying

243
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,760
isn't entirely impossible.

244
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:49,360
If the Marquis House

245
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,560
got their hands on the core technique

246
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,880
for crafting Gambiered Silk,

247
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:54,480
they could absolutely
leverage their influence

248
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,560
and monopolize
the entire Gambiered Silk trade

249
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:56,560
throughout Feng City.

250
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,120
In that case, the Zhous

251
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,760
will quickly fall into decline,

252
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:02,480
maybe even collapse entirely.

253
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:07,160
You promised to pay me 5,000 taels.

254
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:08,240
Not a single tael less.

255
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:09,560
Rest assured,

256
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:11,040
you'll get every last tael.

257
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:12,640
Long,

258
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:14,000
is there truly

259
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,680
no more room for discussion between us?

260
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:18,640
I'm acting under
the Marquis's heir's direct orders.

261
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,080
He wants you dead

262
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,560
or crippled at least, Li Yunhe.

263
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,600
Is that really necessary?

264
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:25,760
I don't think our grudges go that deep.

265
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:28,240
Mr. Lu has his sights set on the Zhous.

266
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:30,760
But you went and became
their live-in son-in-law,

267
00:12:30,760 --> 00:12:31,800
and on top of that,

268
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,280
you've foiled his schemes.

269
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,640
Of course, he wants you dead.

270
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:37,400
But I've already been divorced.

271
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:39,040
I'm long past being
the Zhous' son-in-law.

272
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:40,280
So why is Lu Qifeng

273
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,360
still hounding me so relentlessly?

274
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,760
I don't care about the bad blood

275
00:12:43,760 --> 00:12:44,840
between you two.

276
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:48,160
I get it now.

277
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,360
You've got your own ideas.

278
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,160
Let me hear them.

279
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,840
No wonder they call you a genius,

280
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:55,960
and no wonder you managed

281
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,840
to keep making the Marquis's heir
choke on his own schemes.

282
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:01,000
Since you've laid it all out
in the open,

283
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:03,200
I'll be straight with you too.

284
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,960
This year, Feng City was hit by floods.

285
00:13:05,880 --> 00:13:08,480
Many places have been devastated
by natural disaster.

286
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:11,200
I've handled business
for Mr. Lu For years.

287
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,040
When my hometown was struck,

288
00:13:13,040 --> 00:13:15,120
I wanted to get money from him
for disaster relief.

289
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:16,680
But he took

290
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:18,960
all the money and gambled it
on inflating grain prices

291
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,760
and even ordered me

292
00:13:20,760 --> 00:13:22,760
to sink every last coin of mine
into it as well.

293
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,880
You know
the rest of the story well enough.

294
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:28,360
Grain prices plummeted.

295
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:30,320
The Marquis's House is now piled high

296
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:32,240
with overpriced grain no one will buy.

297
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:34,240
Even if you searched

298
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,840
the entire household,

299
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:37,960
you couldn't
scrape together a single tael.

300
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:40,000
(The Marquis House)

301
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,440
(doesn't even have one tael left?)

302
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:44,360
So, lay it out.

303
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,040
How much do you want?

304
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:47,840
3,000 taels.

305
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,160
Li Yunhe,

306
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,000
don't you try to haggle with me.

307
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:56,160
3,000 taels is my bottom line.

308
00:13:56,560 --> 00:13:58,640
You've handled
so many affairs for the Zhous.

309
00:13:58,640 --> 00:14:00,400
A sum like this is nothing to you.

310
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:01,160
At the very worst,

311
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:03,360
you could sell Xianquan Tavern.

312
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:05,160
That would more than cover it.

313
00:14:06,280 --> 00:14:07,480
There's absolutely no way

314
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:09,360
I'm selling this tavern.

315
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:11,160
What now?

316
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:13,360
So we're done negotiating?

317
00:14:13,680 --> 00:14:14,880
What's the rush?

318
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:16,480
Isn't it just about the money?

319
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:18,640
So how much can you give?

320
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,760
As long as you do exactly as I say,

321
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:22,360
within two hours,

322
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,880
I'll get you 5,000 taels.

323
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:26,000
5,000 taels?

324
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:43,360
- This fight's rigged!
- Pay up!

325
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,960
- Pay up!
- Pay up!

326
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:45,960
- Give me my money back!
- Refund!

327
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,480
- Refund!
- Refund!

328
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:48,680
If this keeps up,

329
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:49,880
they'll be so pissed

330
00:14:49,880 --> 00:14:50,760
that they might fight us.

331
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:51,760
Yeah, you're probably right.

332
00:14:52,040 --> 00:14:52,960
Let's wrap this up then.

333
00:14:57,040 --> 00:14:57,960
What's that?

334
00:15:02,680 --> 00:15:03,760
- Give us our money back!
- Refund!

335
00:15:03,760 --> 00:15:04,760
My grandma could get in the ring

336
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:05,720
- and put up a better fight than them!
- Give me a refund!

337
00:15:06,160 --> 00:15:07,560
This is a fixed fight! Pay up!

338
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:08,880
Go on!

339
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:11,560
- Get up, now! Come on!
- Come on, get up!

340
00:15:11,560 --> 00:15:12,760
What are you even doing?

341
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:14,120
Lift him up there!

342
00:15:14,122 --> 00:15:14,960
Lift him up there!

343
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:15,320
Hurry!

344
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:17,480
Come on!

345
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:18,240
Refund!

346
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:19,760
The Marquis House and Li Yunhe

347
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:20,760
are in cahoots,

348
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:22,880
scamming us out
of our hard-earned money!

349
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:23,840
I want my money back!

350
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,880
- Refund!
- Refund!

351
00:15:25,880 --> 00:15:27,200
- Refund!
- Pay up!

352
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:30,560
- Give us our money back!
- Refund!

353
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:33,240
(Man, gambling is such a rush.)

354
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:34,400
(Bet 1,000 taels on myself)

355
00:15:34,400 --> 00:15:35,160
(at 20-to-1,)

356
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:36,960
(and that's 20,000 taels.)

357
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:38,440
- Pay up!
- Pay up!

358
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:40,000
Li Yunhe wins!

359
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,960
- Pay up!
- Pay up!

360
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:44,640
- Refund!
- Pay up!

361
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:47,880
Li Yunhe!

362
00:15:47,880 --> 00:15:48,560
Oh no,

363
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:49,800
he's hurt! Chunxiang,

364
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:50,680
go find a doctor, quick!

365
00:15:50,680 --> 00:15:51,160
Okay.

366
00:15:51,680 --> 00:15:53,240
Is Li Yunhe just putting on an act?

367
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:54,200
Act, my foot!

368
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:55,080
Get moving!

369
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:55,960
What's going on here?

370
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:01,360
I'm alright.

371
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:05,000
- Pay up!
- Pay up!

372
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:06,400
Hey! Still enjoying

373
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:07,200
the scenery now?

374
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:07,640
- Pay up!
- Pay up, now!

375
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:10,640
- Give me back my money right now!
- Pay up!

376
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:14,160
My apologies,

377
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:15,360
my lord.

378
00:16:15,760 --> 00:16:17,040
I've failed you.

379
00:16:49,940 --> 00:16:53,540
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

380
00:16:53,700 --> 00:16:56,900
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

381
00:16:57,420 --> 00:17:00,140
♪Who took the March rain♪

382
00:17:00,380 --> 00:17:03,740
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

383
00:17:04,100 --> 00:17:06,900
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

384
00:17:07,060 --> 00:17:10,260
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

385
00:17:11,140 --> 00:17:17,060
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

386
00:17:17,100 --> 00:17:20,540
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

387
00:17:20,780 --> 00:17:23,620
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

388
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:26,060
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

389
00:17:26,060 --> 00:17:30,260
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

390
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:33,620
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

391
00:17:33,780 --> 00:17:36,900
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

392
00:17:37,420 --> 00:17:40,340
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

393
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:47,020
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

394
00:18:13,300 --> 00:18:16,820
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

395
00:18:17,060 --> 00:18:20,220
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

396
00:18:20,820 --> 00:18:23,540
♪Who took the March rain♪

397
00:18:23,740 --> 00:18:27,060
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

398
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:30,340
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

399
00:18:30,420 --> 00:18:34,140
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

400
00:18:34,180 --> 00:18:37,460
♪Warp and weft entwine,
one shuttle, one dream♪

401
00:18:37,460 --> 00:18:40,420
♪As seasons change♪

402
00:18:40,420 --> 00:18:44,060
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

403
00:18:44,060 --> 00:18:46,900
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

404
00:18:46,980 --> 00:18:49,540
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

405
00:18:49,540 --> 00:18:53,620
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

406
00:18:53,620 --> 00:18:56,940
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

407
00:18:56,940 --> 00:19:00,660
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

408
00:19:01,060 --> 00:19:04,180
♪Washing away
a lifetime of wear and tear♪

409
00:19:04,180 --> 00:19:07,060
♪Only for you♪

410
00:19:07,060 --> 00:19:10,660
♪On the street of golden honors,
the music rises♪

411
00:19:10,780 --> 00:19:13,540
♪The moon moves west
beyond the pavilion♪

412
00:19:13,660 --> 00:19:16,220
♪Wine runs dry, yet the revelry lingers♪

413
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:20,300
♪In silk, I seek a kindred soul♪

414
00:19:20,300 --> 00:19:23,620
♪The rain has ceased,
clouds begin to clear♪

415
00:19:23,660 --> 00:19:27,020
♪The fragrant silk billows
under the low-hung stars♪

416
00:19:27,860 --> 00:19:33,540
♪I'd cut the clouds and morning glow
to drape over you♪

417
00:19:34,620 --> 00:19:38,740
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

418
00:19:40,020 --> 00:19:44,540
♪Your wedding gown♪
